1
00:00:00,600 --> 00:00:07,400
Hello!
 Here you can get help doing your cases at Försäkringskassan digitally by using Mobile BankID.

2
00:00:08,100 --> 00:00:15,800
With Mobile BankID you can use your phone to log in to My pages on your computer and to log in to the My Page app on your mobile.

3
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:20,320
In six simple steps that only take two minutes, we show how to do it.

4
00:00:21,645 --> 00:00:28,985
Go to your internet bank and order Mobile BankID and download the BankID app for your mobile.

5
00:00:32,980 --> 00:00:37,760
Go to My Pages and click Login.

6
00:00:42,180 --> 00:00:50,940
Click Mobile BankID.

7
00:00:52,162 --> 00:01:01,602
Complete your social security number - twelve digits in a row - and click Login.

8
00:01:02,700 --> 00:01:13,360
You will be asked to start the BankID app on your mobile and then you should identify yourself with your personal code.

9
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:25,040
Now you are on My pages and can apply, report and sign your cases.

10
00:01:26,140 --> 00:01:29,960
Thank you for doing your cases digitally with BankID!

